	<li style="margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Cor da guia: Azul com contas douradas, azul escuro ou amarela (em algumas casas);</span></span></span></span></span></li>
